</entry>
<entry>
<para>Default Value</para>
</entry>
</row>
</thead><tbody>
<row>
<entry>
<para>
<code>pageSize</code>
</para>
</entry>
<entry>
<para>Sets the page size which controls the number of visible child Treeitem. -1 means no limitation.</para>
<para>The default value gets by <code>getTree().getPageSize()</code>
</para>
</entry>
<entry>
<para>
<code>int</code>
</para>
</entry>
<entry>
<para>
<code>10</code>
</para>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<para>
<code>activePage</code>
</para>
</entry>
<entry>
<para>Sets the active page (starting from 0).</para>
</entry>
<entry>
<para>
<code>int</code>
</para>
</entry>
<entry>
<para>0</para>
</entry>
</row></tbody></tgroup>
</informaltable>
